				When you're in the society, you'll get four rolls of top-quality TP deliverd to your door each and every month. Forget the hassle, just sit back, relax and happy wiping.
			</h5>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-5">
			<%= image_tag "4-roll.png", class: "4-roll" %>
		</div>
	</div>
	<hr class="featurette-divider">
	<div class="row featurette">
		<div class="col-md-5">
			<%= image_tag "feeding-america-red.png", class: "4-roll" %>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-7">
			<h4>Wipe Away Hunger.</h4>
			<h5>
				For every shipment we send out, we donate a roll to our friends at Feeding America. Making a difference at home and for America's less fortunate. That's what The Society is all about.
			</h5>
		</div>
	</div>
	<hr class="featurette-divider">
	<div class="row featurette">
		<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
			<%= link_to "Join The Society", register_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg left-right-join" %>
		</div>
	</div>
	</div>
